  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  informed consent

          -  men/women aged 18-85 years

          -  knowledge of the dutch language

          -  hemodialysis patient

          -  subjective sleep problems (Epworth sleepiness score &gt;9)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  known major illness, which interferes with patient's participation

          -  use of melatonin/hypnotics

          -  use of photosensitizing medication

          -  jet lag or travel &gt; 1 time zone
